### Delete a Campaign Reward [DELETE /campaign/{campaign_id}/reward/{reward_id}]

Delete a reward for a given campaign

1. `'reward_id' => '1511l321'`
specified in url.

+ Parameters
    + campaign_id: `1111l123` (required, string)
    + reward_id: `1511l321` (string, required)
    
+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes 
        + reward_id: `1111l123` (string)
        + status: `deleted` (string)
            
+ Response 404 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes
        + error
            + message: `Reward '1511l321' not found for campaign '1111l123'` (string)


## Listing rewards created for a Campaign [/campaign/{campaign_id}/rewards]

The endpoints below list out the rewards that have been created against conversions.

### Conversion Rewards [GET /campaign/{campaign_id}/conversions/rewards]

List all rewards grouped by conversions for a given campaign

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes
        + conversions (array[Conversion Reward])
            
+ Response 404 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes
        + error
            + message: `Campaign not found for id 1111l123` (string)
